<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NEXUS</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="./assets/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/hirePage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="directory">
        <div class="logo-directory">
            <a href=""><img class="logo-top" src="./assets/logo.svg"></a>
            <p>Home/PostPage</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="settings"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">power_settings_new</span></a>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-no-settings">
            <a href="/studentHomePage" class="icon-link "><img class="home icon" src="/assets/home.png"></a>
            <a href="/searchpage" class="icon-link"><img class="search-icon icon"  src="/assets/search.png"></a>
            <a href="/hirePage" class="icon-link open"><img class="search-icon icon" src="/assets/job-icon.png"></a>
            <a href="/notificationPage" class="icon-link"><img class="notifications icon"  src="/assets/bell.png"></a>
            <a href="/collabPage" class="icon-link"><img class="users icon"  src="/assets/users.png"></a>
            <a href="/messagePage" class="icon-link"><img class="messages icon"  src="/assets/send.png"></a>
            <a href="/profilePage" class="icon-link "><img class="profile icon"  src="/assets/profile.png"></a> 
        </div>        
    </div>
    <div class="popup-container" id="popup-container">
        <div class="popup" id="popup">
            <h2>LogOut</h2>
            <p>Are you sure you want to log out?</p>
            <div>
                <a href="landingPage"><button id="logout">Yes</button></a>
                <button id="close-popup">No</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="center">
        <div class="post">
            <div class="head">
                <div class="details">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="name">&nbsp Hemanth</div>
                </div>
                <!-- <div class="follow"><i class="fa-thin fa-plus icon">&nbsp <span>Follow</i></div>  -->
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <img src="./assets/p1.png" alt="Amazon Page">
            </div>
            <div class="features">
                <div class="controls">
                  <label for="like" id="like-btn"></label>
                  <label for="comment" id="comment-btn"></label>
                  <label for="save" id="save-btn"></label>
                </div>
                <div class="liked">
                    <div class="desc">
                        Liked by <span>someone</span> and <span>30 others</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                    <div class="desc title">
                        <p class="project-name">Amazon Clone</p>
                        <p><span class="description">Description</span> <br>
                        To add some CSS and position the button over the image, you can set the image container to a relative 
                        position and set the button to an absolute position with a z-index higher than the image. 
                        Adjust the . image-container width and height properties to match the size of your image.</p>
                    </div> 
                    <label for="comment" id="comment-btn2">View all comments </label>
            </div>
            <div class="post-comment">
                <div class="head">
                    <div class="name">
                        Comments
                    </div>
                    <label for="comment" id="comment-btn3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <div class="comments">

                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic.jpeg" alt="">
                        <span>Q2.  Implement a basic
                            calculator application with a clean User Interface of your choice based on
                            following the MVC framework design pattern and involving EJS concept.
                        <div class="desc">2m ago <span> Reply</span></div>
                    </span>
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt="">
                        <span>Q2.  Implement a basic
                            calculator application with a clean User Interface of your choice based on
                            following the MVC framework design pattern and involving EJS concept.
                        <div class="desc">2m ago <span> Reply</span></div>
                    </span>
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt="">
                        <span>Q2.  Implement a basic
                            calculator application with a clean User Interface of your choice based on
                            following the MVC framework design pattern and involving EJS concept.
                        <div class="desc">2m ago <span> Reply</span></div>
                    </span>
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="new-comment">
                    <img src="./assets/profile-pic2.png" alt=""/> &nbsp
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Add a Comment...."/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="./js/hirePage.js"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/6953004357.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>